name: Well Guarded (V)
Lore: 'Most of Jabba''s guards had been sold to the Hutt and were too scared (or too dumb) to leave. Jabba assigned his best guards to watch over his most prized possessions.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Non-unique aliens are immune to Grimtaash (While you have < 13 cards in hand) , The Camp, and deployment conditions on Watch Your Step. During battle with two non-unique aliens of your Rep''s species, your aliens there may not have their forfeit reduced. (Immune to Alter.)',
